{"tid":2400091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法國總統馬克龍警告：中國疫苗效力不明，恐導致更多變種病毒","createTime":"2021-02-08T15:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T02:08:20.000Z","uid":261647,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f8d043381b4b0489b2b316cc9c2412af87b1e115","tid":2400091,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:45:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dw.com/zh/a-56491828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fzh%2Fa-56491828&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMLY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=937425c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dw.com/zh/a-56491828</a><br />\n<br />\n就在世界各國陸陸續續收到大批中國疫苗的同時，法國總統馬克宏提醒，這些有效率低的中國疫苗可能會對防疫帶來反效果。<br />\n<br />\n國藥集團12月表示，其疫苗的有效率低於西方輝瑞（Pfizer-BioNTech）疫苗和摩德納公司（Moderna）疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n盡管中國政府沒有公布任何詳細的臨床試驗數據，但一再堅持認為這種注射劑是安全有效的。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，盡管與其他疫苗相比，中國疫苗的療效令人擔憂，柬埔寨等國依舊決定接受北京饋贈。<br />\n<br />\n根據法新社，法國總統馬克宏在2月4日對中國新冠疫苗缺乏資訊的情況提出警告，稱如果這些疫苗無效，甚至會導致更多變種病毒出現。<br />\n<br />\n他說，由於中國「完全沒有分享任何有關試驗的信息」，因此來自國藥或科興苗的療效還不得而知。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「這意味著，從中長期來看，幾乎可以肯定，如果這種疫苗不合適，將促進新的變種病毒的出現，這樣絕對不會解決這些國家的情況，」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/法國/20210204-馬克龍-中國現階段新冠疫苗不透明\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%2F20210204-%E9%A6%AC%E5%85%8B%E9%BE%8D-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%8F%BE%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%8F%E6%98%8E&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMLY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=63842914\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/法國/20210204-馬克龍-中國現階段新冠疫苗不透明</a><br />\n<br />\n巴西北部地區馬瑙斯（Manaus）和亞馬遜（Amazon）變種病毒已佔了主體。法國總統馬克龍在大西洋理事會(Atlantic Council)智囊團上表示：這意味着，不論是從中期還是長期來看，幾乎可以確定，中國現階段的疫苗不僅不合用；而且它還會導致新的變異病毒。這意味着從中長期來看，幾乎可以確定，當這種疫苗不適用的時候，它絕對不會解決已採用中國疫苗國家的現狀。<br />\n<br />\n法國總統表示，巴西就是一個很好的例子。在馬瑙斯（Manaus）區域，有感染的病患；有接過疫苗的人；還有人出現了新的病情。"},{"pid":"56f56e003d489d7329a1df77982cbd6c770a6c53","tid":2400091,"uid":271516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:48:32.000Z","msg":"有無法國官方原文"},{"pid":"427a2fe7b4b1efd24dc7a7cb22b86360822038e0","tid":2400091,"uid":13663,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T16:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MX5vMvU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMX5vMvU.gif&h=f680446f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4828aa38c684c4ed6cd6b74169858dfb4d7bde57","tid":2400091,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T01:59:21.000Z","msg":"等睇武肺強勢回歸祖國懷抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae52b0309dc4ce082aa0b44387b54c18a04ae835","tid":2400091,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T02:01:13.000Z","msg":"盡管中國政府沒有公布任何詳細的臨床試驗數據，但一再堅持認為這種注射劑是安全有效的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁都打就真係白皮豬"},{"pid":"38869eb57f7717b7fd54981f8f19137e63c319ce","tid":2400091,"uid":129658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae52b0309dc4ce082aa0b44387b54c18a04ae835","tid":2400091,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T02:01:13.000Z","msg":"盡管中國政府沒有公布任何詳細的臨床試驗數據，但一再堅持認為這種注射劑是安全有效的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁都打就真係白皮豬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T02:08:20.000Z","msg":"隻藥無試過，但放心絕對無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}